The authors also mention the use of graph representations in computer vision (cs.CV) and social network analysis (cs.SI), which are subfields of computer science that often involve graph data. Additionally, the paper discusses the need for rigorous experimental procedures and reproducibility, which are topics related to natural language processing (cs.CL) and other areas of computer science research.
